Comment: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:10.31,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,It's hot! It's hot! It's hot!
Comment: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Comment: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Comment: 0,0:00:10.31,0:00:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,

Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.04,0:01:49.59,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Once upon a time, there lived\Na grandmother and a grandfather.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.59,0:01:52.47,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,The weather's great today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.47,0:01:54.60,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Sakura Baa-san went to the river to do the laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.24,0:01:58.31,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Yukimura Jii-san went to the mountain to get firewood...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.31,0:02:01.19,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,which was what he was supposed to do,\Nbut instead he was helping with the laundry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.37,0:02:05.65,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Then all of a sudden, a large peach came drifting down the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.65,0:02:07.36,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,What is this!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.36,0:02:10.38,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,Yay, I love peaches!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.38,0:02:11.53,Default,Yuk,0000,0000,0000,,Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.53,0:02:15.70,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Grandmother and Grandfather took the peach home and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.70,0:02:16.99,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,Shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:18.60,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Tried to eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.60,0:02:19.62,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Right then-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.05,0:02:28.80,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,From the peach, came out-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.80,0:02:30.76,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.76,0:02:40.23,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,I-I am... will... slay the Oni!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.09,0:02:47.38,Default,Yuk,0000,0000,0000,,Granny! A person came out of the peach!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.38,0:02:50.53,Default,Yuk,0000,0000,0000,,It's no time to be eating the peach.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.53,0:02:56.20,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that the Oni are kidnapping young girls; terrifying the villagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.20,0:03:00.36,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,My, what a fine child we have here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:04.59,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Those atrocious Oni! Unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.42,0:03:07.60,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, Peach Boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.60,0:03:11.28,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,Act naturally and you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.96,0:03:13.57,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.57,0:03:16.68,Default,Yuk,0000,0000,0000,,Granny. When did you come up with the name?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.39,0:03:19.81,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Grandfather and Grandmother. I'll be off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.81,0:03:24.88,Default,Suk,0000,0000,0000,,You're kinda hot, so take these with you. It's on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.88,0:03:27.11,Default,Suk,0000,0000,0000,,Eat a lot of kibi-dango.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.11,0:03:28.71,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Grandmother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.34,0:03:30.65,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Take care!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.65,0:03:33.33,Default,Suk,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.16,0:03:35.86,Default,Yuk,0000,0000,0000,,What was this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.86,0:03:39.25,Default,Suk,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know. Let's eat the peach.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.25,0:03:43.54,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,As such, Peach Boy went to slay the Oni and-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.87,0:03:48.55,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,he found Dog, Pheasant, and Monkey.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.55,0:03:50.42,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Why are we putting up with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.42,0:03:53.05,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault, Dog! You got tricked by that guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.05,0:03:54.65,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,So did you, Monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:56.20,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for not noticing, Pheasant!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.20,0:03:58.32,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,I told you it was suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.76,0:04:00.85,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,What are you guys doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:03.31,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Good Samaritan there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.31,0:04:04.27,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Please help us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.27,0:04:07.00,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to get killed after being tricked by a villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.06,0:04:16.61,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Peach Boy saved the three who said they would do anything if he saved them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:22.37,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,But they tried to snag the kibi-dango from him, so he punished them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.37,0:04:25.33,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,See? That's why I had them tied up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:34.50,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,That's the bad guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.58,0:04:37.47,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:40.80,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Usui.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.71,0:04:44.18,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the Ring Master of the Moron Trio Circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.18,0:04:45.93,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,That's our members.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.93,0:04:47.01,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,So fishy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.21,0:04:57.94,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,I went and started a circus group, but they're useless, so I was just planning to eat them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.94,0:04:59.36,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.36,0:05:02.36,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,If you're going to kill them\Nfor food's sake, then I can't stop you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:03.86,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.86,0:05:06.72,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,We've only been practicing, so we ran out of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.72,0:05:10.76,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,All the "training" was you whipping us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:11.71,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.63,0:05:13.71,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,who should I start with?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.71,0:05:15.46,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,I don't taste good!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.46,0:05:16.63,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,He's really tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.63,0:05:17.38,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,No, he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:18.84,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.84,0:05:20.94,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,You're the yummiest!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.34,0:05:22.01,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:24.17,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Please help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.17,0:05:26.62,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Before you get eaten, I want to ask one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.62,0:05:28.75,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you won't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.75,0:05:30.23,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know where the Oni are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:32.19,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,No, we don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.19,0:05:33.03,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:37.27,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Usui, if you can't pick one,\NI recommend mixing them in a soup.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.27,0:05:38.32,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,I'm off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.82,0:05:42.59,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.59,0:05:46.91,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know where the Oni live, but I do know a village where Oni appeared recently!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.38,0:05:54.63,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,It's a village with many young people, but the day after the Oni came, all the girls were missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.63,0:05:55.75,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Which village is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.75,0:05:58.75,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,We'll take you there if you save us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.33,0:06:03.55,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Usui...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.20,0:06:05.05,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:08.18,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,But instead-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.17,0:06:10.89,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a kibi-dango.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.48,0:06:19.69,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx92}And so the Peach Boy departed to search the Oni with Dog, Monkey, Pheasant, and a sketchy Ring Master of a circus group.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.69,0:06:21.36,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Where's our share of kibi-dango?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:22.92,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,I ate them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.92,0:06:23.87,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,D'oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.87,0:06:27.15,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,But, this is kinda nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.15,0:06:30.04,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a party led by a hero out to defeat evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:31.98,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Party?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:35.89,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,You're nuts! Do you think this is some kind of fun activity?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:38.01,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,We're not on a field trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.01,0:06:39.75,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,It's not that kind of "party"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.75,0:06:41.92,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,It means "a group of people that travel together to achieve a common goal"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.40,0:06:45.86,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,So something like that is necessary, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:47.56,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,In that case-
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.56,0:06:49.59,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be a party that slays Oni!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.59,0:06:51.41,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,In short, we're the "Oni Slay Party"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.41,0:06:53.61,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,It's a great name. Any objections?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.61,0:06:54.85,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Good, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.38,0:07:04.70,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,So it's here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.72,0:07:08.62,Note,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Flag: Oni Slay Party
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:08.10,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,The village where the Oni kidnapped all the girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.29,0:07:14.33,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,It's completely tattered. I don't sense a soul here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.72,0:07:17.54,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,I said that's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.54,0:07:18.71,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,You plan on snatching it away from me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.71,0:07:21.05,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,That was the last one that grew from my farm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.05,0:07:23.53,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's from my farm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.19,0:07:27.50,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:28.46,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:29.31,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:32.81,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:35.31,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,What I see here happened because of Oni?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.23,0:07:37.90,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Something stinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.73,0:07:41.20,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.20,0:07:44.22,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,He ran away because of the smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:46.70,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Dog has a good sense of smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.72,0:07:53.56,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If you can't tolerate that level of smell, I suggest you leave this village now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:54.95,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.95,0:08:02.12,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,This is no longer a village any sane human can live in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.99,0:08:05.42,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What happened? Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.53,0:08:09.68,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, so they're out of the race, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:11.51,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Care to explain?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.51,0:08:15.56,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,You see, none of us bathe anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:19.86,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,After the girls went missing,\Nlaundry and housekeeping all went downhill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:22.81,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,All the guys are going through a survival-mode lifestyle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:25.36,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,This is more like a war zone than a village.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.10,0:08:28.87,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,The law of the jungle applies here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.87,0:08:32.49,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,But life in survival-mode is pretty fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.49,0:08:33.58,Default,Guys,0000,0000,0000,,It's really thrilling.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:39.62,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do with the village like this when the girls come back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.63,0:08:42.34,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,They won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.34,0:08:44.61,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, we're talking about Oni.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.61,0:08:47.02,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way we can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.02,0:08:47.93,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.93,0:08:49.95,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Cut that crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:53.65,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go save the girls, so tell me where the Oni are!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.06,0:08:58.23,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,It's so peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.04,0:09:06.24,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,So the Oni Island is beyond this ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.24,0:09:08.32,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,I can only see the horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.32,0:09:11.08,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Can we trust those villagers?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.08,0:09:14.75,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,They sounded so irresponsible!\NThey had no intention of helping us out!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.75,0:09:17.07,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,It totally looked like we were bothering them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.00,0:09:19.16,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:21.14,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't go today!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.14,0:09:23.38,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,We might get different information from another village.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:24.34,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.34,0:09:25.55,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Bon voyage!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.55,0:09:27.69,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't listen to us...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.69,0:09:29.12,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,What is this turtle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:30.75,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Let's flip it on its back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:31.76,Default,Kids,0000,0000,0000,,Do it, do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.76,0:09:34.04,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.04,0:09:35.39,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:38.30,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,He saved the turtle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:40.30,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Could this lead to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.30,0:09:41.06,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Lead to?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.06,0:09:44.63,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard of a story that goes like this:
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.63,0:09:52.02,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,If you save a turtle, to show its gratitude, it puts you on its shell and takes you to the palace under the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.02,0:09:54.21,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Palace? What's this place like?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.21,0:10:04.55,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx92}The sexy Otohime-sama will serve you with plenty of seafood like sea bream and tuna, and will even give you a souvenir to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.55,0:10:06.54,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously? Let's have it take us there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.54,0:10:11.47,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,But you must be careful of the box she gives you as a souvenir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:17.60,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,When you open it, smoke will come out and you will turn into an old man in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.60,0:10:20.39,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Why does she give out such a dangerous object?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.39,0:10:22.36,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Is the turtle trying to repay kindness with ingratitude?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:25.62,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Wait. Should we just leave that box unopened?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:26.93,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.93,0:10:32.76,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't open the box, we get to feast out and have fun with the hot and sexy Otohime-sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.76,0:10:35.70,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,You guys. Why are you talking so secretively?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:36.91,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Yikes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.91,0:10:38.80,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.52,0:10:43.20,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go to Oni Island on this turtle's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.20,0:10:45.13,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,We'll lead the way and check things out.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.13,0:10:47.34,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:52.20,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this about to turn into a separate story?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:53.47,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:02.69,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,I can't breathe!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.69,0:11:03.57,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Was it trying to kill us?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.57,0:11:05.11,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,I can't swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.27,0:11:09.59,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Will we be fine with this puny boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.59,0:11:12.74,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do if we get stranded? We don't even have any food.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.74,0:11:14.78,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,If that happens, we'll eat you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.56,0:11:16.57,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,We knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:20.05,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Pheasant! You go find the Oni Island from the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.05,0:11:21.16,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.31,0:11:27.97,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,We can't see any land...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.97,0:11:29.42,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Pheasant isn't returning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.42,0:11:31.69,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,He probably ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.69,0:11:34.03,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Our bond is tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.03,0:11:36.68,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,You guys were offering each other when you were about to get eaten.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.68,0:11:38.52,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.52,0:11:40.13,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.13,0:11:42.84,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,How could he run away alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:47.48,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hungry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.48,0:11:48.27,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Me too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:52.99,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Look, I had one left.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.99,0:11:54.99,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,It's mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.99,0:11:55.20,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.20,0:11:56.52,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.33,0:12:15.47,Default,Suz,0000,0000,0000,,Did you guys drop this normal kibi-dango?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.47,0:12:20.15,Default,Suz,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it this stack of postcards that could win you a year's worth of kibi-dango?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:27.60,Default,Suz,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx87}Or, is it this postcard that could win you the Hokkaido Sea Food Set\Nthat gives you king crab, sea urchin, salmon roe, and scallops?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.26,0:12:33.10,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Um, that normal kibi-dango.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.10,0:12:36.85,Default,Suz,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You're an honest man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.85,0:12:41.48,Default,Suz,0000,0000,0000,,As a prize, I'll give you this postcard\Nthat could win you the Hokkaido Sea Food Set.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:45.13,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the postbox?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:48.72,Default,Suz,0000,0000,0000,,There's one in the village by the ocean, 30km from here due north-west-north.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.72,0:12:50.32,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,When do we get the prize?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:52.02,Default,Suz,0000,0000,0000,,The drawing is in a month.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:54.27,Default,Suz,0000,0000,0000,,The winner will be notified through the actual mailing of the prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.40,0:13:00.64,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,She got away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.76,0:13:03.21,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Give back the kibi-dango!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:04.56,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,What are you eating?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.52,0:13:07.01,Default,Yuk,0000,0000,0000,,Shizuko Baa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.01,0:13:08.96,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,Have a peach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.47,0:13:30.40,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Prez.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.92,0:13:32.25,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sleepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.73,0:13:34.09,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Get some rest then.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.09,0:13:36.10,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,I'll stay up for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.97,0:13:39.04,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.04,0:13:40.17,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:46.87,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,I'm traveling with you guys from a turn of events, but I don't trust you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.87,0:13:49.75,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Especially, you, Usui! You're too suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:51.87,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Inner side, the looks, and everything else are!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.05,0:13:55.65,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Then do as you please.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.65,0:13:57.49,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.49,0:13:59.44,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:01.36,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Pheasant?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:04.78,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,He's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.78,0:14:08.22,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Help me! Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.26,0:14:10.16,Default-alt,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,I see something like a rope coming out of Pheasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.38,0:14:15.56,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.72,0:14:22.51,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Help me! They're going to kill us!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.51,0:14:26.52,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,You know? I bet he picked up a stranded ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:29.83,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,How considerate of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.83,0:14:33.73,Default,Iga,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? So your friends are the ones I see on that cheap boat?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:35.61,Default,Iga,0000,0000,0000,,What a letdown.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.61,0:14:40.82,Default,Iga,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I can get much out of them,\Nso I hope you'll let me have some fun at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.11,0:14:45.74,Default,Iga,0000,0000,0000,,To start things out, beg for your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.74,0:14:46.82,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,You stupid Pheasant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.82,0:14:48.47,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get captured by a pirate!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.47,0:14:49.60,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,You should have sacrificed yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:51.00,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,You heartless bunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.40,0:14:57.76,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.76,0:14:58.72,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the turtle from before?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.72,0:15:00.67,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it came to say thank you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:08.06,Default,Aoi,0000,0000,0000,,Would you promise not to look inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.06,0:15:09.26,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Sure! Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.35,0:15:17.23,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Mustn't peek! She must have brought an amazing weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.74,0:15:21.06,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't this about to turn into another story again?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:22.19,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.81,0:15:35.04,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,What is she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.50,0:15:39.30,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,A mysterious guy is sleeping there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.30,0:15:40.34,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Who is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.34,0:15:41.41,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.34,0:15:45.68,Default,Iga,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of a stupid skit was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.68,0:15:46.84,Default,Iga,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.84,0:15:49.18,Default,Shi,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you were enjoying the peaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.18,0:15:51.04,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,We still have plenty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.04,0:15:52.91,Default,Sak,0000,0000,0000,,Eat all the peaches you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.91,0:15:54.31,Default,Yuk,0000,0000,0000,,Granny...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:15:56.69,Default,Iga,0000,0000,0000,,I can't play along with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.40,0:16:04.24,Default,Iga,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So you sliced the bullet with your sword?{the built?}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.33,0:16:10.91,Default,Iga,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting. You come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.24,0:16:14.96,Default,Iga,0000,0000,0000,,Come up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.34,0:16:22.75,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Oh fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:28.63,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,No, that's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.63,0:16:31.34,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,I suggest you plug your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:39.86,Default,Iga,0000,0000,0000,,This ship is really flammable!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.06,0:16:47.45,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.45,0:16:48.78,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.62,0:16:52.12,Default,Iga,0000,0000,0000,,What an interesting bunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.07,0:17:01.38,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,T-Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.03,0:17:03.57,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,My pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:08.55,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,On another note, it's morning already.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.55,0:17:10.39,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.77,0:17:18.23,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.45,0:17:22.48,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,So it finally appears.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.66,0:17:24.85,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Oni Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.61,0:17:32.28,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can we really beat them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.28,0:17:34.37,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,We don't even have a weapon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.37,0:17:38.01,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,I know! At a time like this, we'll use that little trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.01,0:17:39.62,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,What little trick?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.62,0:17:41.71,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.21,0:17:43.09,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,A straw?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.09,0:17:45.45,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to trade this with one thing after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.45,0:17:49.14,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a straw now, but eventually, it'll turn into an amazing weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.14,0:17:50.08,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:52.84,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,You got anything to trade this with to start it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.97,0:17:55.06,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:56.46,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, next!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.46,0:17:57.14,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.14,0:17:59.23,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.23,0:18:00.67,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, next!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.67,0:18:01.46,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.46,0:18:03.21,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:04.36,Default-alt,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,These are all the weapons we need!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:05.82,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go straight in!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:08.65,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Prez, check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.36,0:18:11.74,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.26,0:18:15.93,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,So, we sneak in pretending\Nwe want to become a part of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.93,0:18:20.62,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,The girls may not have to face danger this way, compared to busting in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:26.39,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,This could be a trap in itself, but let's try getting changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.39,0:18:27.89,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.89,0:18:29.82,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,We'll go scout things in a realistic version.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.82,0:18:31.42,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,We'll pretend to be wild animals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:37.59,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,If it doesn't look like we've got any chance, let's get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.59,0:18:38.60,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,What does it look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.05,0:18:42.06,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.69,0:18:50.99,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,It's a paradise!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.55,0:18:56.00,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,It's a maid harem!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.92,0:19:00.33,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget our mission, Moron Trio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.82,0:19:03.79,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,We need to quickly evacuate the girls to a safe place!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:06.19,Default,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,What is this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.19,0:19:07.52,Default,Hon,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a new girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.52,0:19:09.00,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Prez!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.00,0:19:11.46,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,You were a girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:14.82,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Let's forget about these guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.82,0:19:16.64,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Usui go to?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.64,0:19:17.76,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.00,0:19:26.88,Default,Maids,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.59,0:19:43.33,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Usui... You're....
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.73,0:19:45.54,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,You were fooling me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.54,0:19:48.19,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Did I not say that I'm an Oni?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.19,0:19:50.95,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,But I am the Ring Master of the Moron Trio Circus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:52.79,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I've heard that already!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.79,0:19:55.59,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,So it was you who kidnapped all these girls, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:19:57.87,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare yourself, you perv Oni!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.01,0:20:02.17,Default,Hon,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. What kind of wrong idea are you getting?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.56,0:20:05.64,Default,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,We live here out of our own choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:06.89,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.89,0:20:10.24,Default,Sub,0000,0000,0000,,I was getting fed up with the lifestyle there.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.24,0:20:12.28,Default,Eri,0000,0000,0000,,The guys were dirty and selfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.28,0:20:15.16,Default,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,A good-looking guy showed up, so we followed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:17.29,Default,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Then we found this island pretty cozy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.29,0:20:19.51,Default,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,It's comfortable living and our eyes are constantly pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.51,0:20:21.20,Default,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,We're so happy right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.73,0:20:25.41,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,So they took over my house.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.95,0:20:27.56,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,How pitiful I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:31.13,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,So-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.28,0:20:36.04,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, Prez.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:40.69,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Let's leave this island and find some interesting place.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.35,0:20:45.38,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying!? Why should I go with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.38,0:20:47.66,Default,Chi,0000,0000,0000,,Flowers of moe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.66,0:20:48.85,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:54.48,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Because it turns me on to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.21,0:20:58.45,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Thus, the two started dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.45,0:21:01.76,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Hold on! I haven't yet-
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:03.02,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Wait, "yet" what?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.02,0:21:07.04,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1}Anyway, I have no intention\Nto be with a perv like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.76,0:21:05.66,Default-alt,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}You know, Prez,\Nyou look so seductive in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.66,0:21:07.04,Default-alt,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3}Look at that bare leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.04,0:21:10.57,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,No! I ripped the bottom because I thought I was going to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.05,0:21:16.21,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,The two set off on a new trip together, but that's a whole different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:16.38,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,{\alpha&HFF&}PLACEHOLDER
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:17.21,Default-alt,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,Let go!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:18.57,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,All is well that ends well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.59,0:21:26.06,Default,Mis,0000,0000,0000,,No. Stop it, you perv!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.56,0:21:31.68,Default,Yuk,0000,0000,0000,,Usui-san, what are you making Prez listen to?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.68,0:21:33.93,Default,Yuk,0000,0000,0000,,She looks like she's having a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.93,0:21:36.23,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,My special folk tale.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.14,0:21:41.27,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, the Moron Trio ends up as the two's dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:43.06,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,but that's a whole different story as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.06,0:21:45.58,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,We were food until the end...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.58,0:21:46.60,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.60,0:21:47.61,Default,Trio,0000,0000,0000,,It's horrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.61,0:21:51.68,Default,Usu,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Then the Trio lived safe and sound.
